channel.title: Fully Working Server Compiler and Server Runner
channel.description:
this is pureman0194's compiler. I made a few changes. I added some lines of code to allow it to support newer versions of java sdk. It now supports up to java sdk 6 update 7 instead of only update 5. If your compiler doesn't work just dl this one and replace your old one with it. Can an admin or mod sticky this, I think this is very helpfull since a lot of people are have problems with compilers.
http://filebeam.com/d506f2fbf99fa10c990a0948d59c2fe9 - This is the dl link (the compiler is fixed and will now run your server)
Thank me for the upload plz - any problems let me know and i'll see if i can fix them
